DESCRIPTION: A stylish and modern 2-bedroom apartment located in the heart of the city. This property features a spacious living area, open-plan kitchen with contemporary finishes, two full bathrooms, and a private balcony with skyline views. Ideal for professionals or small families.

A luxurious 4-bedroom villa with a landscaped garden, large terrace, and covered parking. Includes a spacious living room, formal dining area, modern kitchen with island, and ensuite master bedroom. Perfect for families seeking comfort and space in a prestigious neighborhood.

A premium 3-bedroom apartment within a gated community offering amenities such as a swimming pool, gym, and concierge services. Features a bright interior, fully fitted kitchen, two bathrooms, and a secure underground parking bay. Walking distance to shops and the beach.

A stunning beach-facing apartment offering panoramic sea views, floor-to-ceiling windows, and modern interiors. This 2-bedroom unit comes with high-end appliances, open-plan living space, and direct beach access. Perfect for seaside living.

Fully furnished 3-bedroom villa featuring an open layout, sleek kitchen, maid’s room, and private patio area. Situated in a quiet, family-friendly community with close proximity to international schools and parks.

A state-of-the-art office unit located in the city's primary business district. Features modern fittings, private meeting rooms, high-speed internet wiring, and security access. Ideal for startups or growing companies.
A contemporary 1-bedroom apartment in a newly developed complex, featuring an open kitchen-living layout, a walk-in closet, and balcony. Ideal for first-time buyers or as an investment opportunity.
This 4-bedroom family home boasts spacious rooms, modern bathrooms, a large outdoor area, and an indoor majlis. Includes a covered garage and is close to local amenities and public transport.
A furnished 2-bedroom apartment overlooking the marina, featuring large windows, an open-plan layout, and elegant furnishings. Amenities include a pool, fitness center, and 24-hour security.
Flexible open-plan commercial space in a newly developed building. Ideal for co-working, retail, or creative agencies. Includes pantry space, two washrooms, and elevator access.
An elegant 3-bedroom house with a rooftop terrace, ideal for gatherings and entertaining. Includes an open kitchen with granite countertops, modern fittings, and ample storage space throughout.
A cozy and affordable 1-bedroom apartment perfect for young professionals or couples. Comes with a bright living space, open kitchen, modern bathroom, and secure entry.
A sleek and contemporary 2-bedroom apartment with bright interiors, built-in wardrobes, and a balcony offering city views. Conveniently located near shopping centers and public transport.
A versatile retail or office unit in a high-footfall location. Features large display windows, modern interiors, and ample parking space for clients.
This grand 5-bedroom villa is surrounded by a private garden and features expansive interiors, a large kitchen with island, multiple living spaces, and private quarters for domestic staff.
A modern studio loft designed with functionality in mind. Offers high ceilings, open-plan layout, and minimalistic interiors perfect for individuals or couples seeking a stylish home.
A 2-bedroom high-rise apartment in a prestigious building with elevator access, basement parking, and 24-hour security. Includes a modern kitchen, large living area, and elegant bathrooms.
Eco-conscious 3-bedroom villa fitted with solar panels, sustainable finishes, and water-efficient landscaping. Includes an open kitchen and green-certified appliances.
A newly built 3-bedroom apartment within a secure, family-oriented complex featuring a swimming pool, children’s play area, and gym. Well-ventilated with modern interiors.
This high-end corporate office spans 2500 sqft and features multiple meeting rooms, high-speed cabling, private restrooms, and city views through panoramic windows.
Located in a peaceful neighborhood, this 4-bedroom villa offers a private yard, spacious interiors, traditional design touches, and ample parking. Ideal for growing families.
A well-appointed 1-bedroom apartment with built-in appliances, efficient layout, and walking access to shops and cafés. Includes basement parking and 24/7 security.
A beautifully designed apartment suite near the government offices. Offers two spacious bedrooms, a large lounge, stylish kitchen, and ample storage space.
A tastefully designed 4-bedroom home with a sunlit atrium, modern kitchen, and elegant finishes. Includes an outdoor BBQ space and upstairs lounge area.
A modern, move-in-ready office space equipped with conference rooms, ergonomic desks, pantry, and private entrance. Excellent for established businesses.
This spacious 5-bedroom villa is located near a tranquil lagoon and offers a perfect blend of nature and luxury. Features include a private pool, gourmet kitchen, and lush outdoor seating areas.
